# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# combined — __enter__, __exit__, __call__ across representative io subjects
#
# 8 classes x 3 methods = 24 rows.
# All three operators are absent from all io subclass __dict__s: all false.
# __enter__ and __exit__ are defined on io.IOBase and inherited; __call__
# is not part of the io stream protocol at any level.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

